00:07:39.352 --> 00:07:43.082
And you're about to see something that you're going to go, 'shock and awe'time.

00:07:43.083 --> 00:07:48.949
I'm just telling you when I'm praying into it, I try to encourage you.

00:07:48.950 --> 00:07:56.038
I was a janitor for 17 years. Worked for a big ministry in Fort Worth.

00:07:56.039 --> 00:08:05.519
Worked for a church for a long time cleaning their houses, cleaning their planes, cleaning things, and just staying faithful to what God told me to do.

00:08:05.520 --> 00:08:14.159
And he said, "I want you to go on YouTube."I thought, "What in the world?"I resisted this for over a year.

00:08:14.160 --> 00:08:27.529
He told me during COVID, at the beginning of it, "I want you to go on YouTube."I said, "No, I don't want to go on YouTube."I was sitting at a Homeland grocery store.

00:08:27.530 --> 00:08:38.779
Now it's a Sack 'n Save or something in Guthrie, Oklahoma. I sat there in that parking lot and I was looking at the Baptist church.

00:08:38.780 --> 00:08:44.799
I'll never forget; I was watching the Baptist church there, and there's a funeral home across the street.

00:08:44.800 --> 00:08:52.730
I sat out there and I was just praying for the city because there's so much witchcraft in Guthrie because of that Masonic Temple.

00:08:52.731 --> 00:09:01.919
I was sitting there and just interceding, and the Lord told me, "I've called you to healing ministry. I've called you to do things for me.

00:09:01.920 --> 00:09:21.278
Are you going to say yes to me?"He said, "If you don't say yes to me, Brandon, it's opening doors for disobedience and you're going to come home early."There will be people that don't want to hear that, but I saw my life being cut short through some things.

00:09:21.279 --> 00:09:26.159
And the Lord said, "You'll go home early."I sat there and he said, "Will you yield to what I've called you to do?

00:09:26.160 --> 00:09:34.593
There's a hedge of protection when you're in obedience."When you're in disobedience to what God has called you to do, there are doors that open.

00:09:34.594 --> 00:09:43.939
And the enemy will oblige the doors and he'll go, "I'm going to kill."He's a kill, steal, and destroy devil. He's looking for an inroad to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:09:43.940 --> 00:09:50.958
But if you're underneath that covering and that shelter of the secret place in that secret place, there's no weapon formed against you that will prosper.

00:09:50.959 --> 00:09:58.319
But that's in obedience. Staying obedient to what God has assigned you to do.

00:09:58.320 --> 00:10:04.239
There's a covering in obedience. You need to know that there is a covering in obedience.

00:10:04.240 --> 00:10:10.918
The blood covers, but a curse without a cause cannot stand. Most people don't understand that.

00:10:10.919 --> 00:10:17.279
People go, "Are you concerned about witches and warlocks and everybody trying to curse you?"No, not even a little bit.

00:10:17.280 --> 00:10:25.138
I believe in the power of the covenant. I believe in what he said he'd do for me—that as he is, so are we in this world.

00:10:25.139 --> 00:10:35.953
And that comes out of staying in the place of protection. Where is your place of protection? Staying in obedience.

00:10:35.954 --> 00:10:43.984
When he said, "I want you to go to the little church in Colville,"well, I get offered to go to a big church in Miami.

00:10:43.985 --> 00:10:50.591
I can go anywhere I want to go and have a platform if I wanted to in the natural because of how big what God has done here.

00:10:50.592 --> 00:10:58.570
But he said, "I want you to stay at the covering here right now."Well, I think it'd be a good idea to go over here.

00:10:58.571 --> 00:11:03.129
He didn't say do that. There's a place of protection and obedience.

00:11:03.130 --> 00:11:11.518
No matter what you think in your mind, you follow the voice. For those that are led by the Spirit of God are the sons of God.

00:11:11.519 --> 00:11:17.159
So when you're led by the Spirit of God, it doesn't have to make sense.

00:11:17.160 --> 00:11:25.039
Just say, "Okay."I'm trying to tell you that there is a place of protection and obedience.

00:11:25.040 --> 00:11:31.759
You've got to stay obedient to what God has called you to do. You know how long I wanted to quit that job at the church cleaning toilets?

00:11:31.760 --> 00:11:51.759
Even when Diana was doing full-time eBay and doing things, I thought, "I'm ready to get out of here."And we kept building the business, and she finally—the Lord told me she was to quit full-time.

00:11:51.760 --> 00:12:02.699
I got laid off. She was still doing little things here and there and the Lord said, "Now is the time I want you to step out by faith."I was so freaked out because we didn't have benefits.

00:12:02.700 --> 00:12:06.638
I'm telling you, I was scared because I thought, "We need medical.

00:12:06.639 --> 00:12:12.239
Oh my goodness, we need medical,"because the church had medical and I was able to be underneath our plan at that time.

00:12:12.240 --> 00:12:25.428
I was so freaked out. I said, "Oh, no. We don't have medical."In your mind, you always have so much thinking that is so small and it's poverty.

00:12:25.429 --> 00:12:32.408
Then I started thinking, "Well, my kids need medical."We know all this stuff. What are we going to do?

00:12:32.409 --> 00:12:39.999
