00:12:40.000 --> 00:12:51.919
Being in the place called 'there,'when the Riverbrook dries up, like I told you a couple of broadcasts ago, when the Riverbrook dries up, God will always take you to the place of your next provision.

00:12:51.920 --> 00:12:58.718
God is not a God of lack; he's a God of more than enough. And he will always provide for his kids.

00:12:58.719 --> 00:13:04.170
I believe that just like the Bible said: I've never seen the righteous forsaken or his seed begging bread.

00:13:04.171 --> 00:13:10.078
So wherever your place of 'there'is, wherever he's called you to be, there will always be a supply.

00:13:10.079 --> 00:13:15.519
It may not be the abundance that you want at that time, but it will get you through.

00:13:15.520 --> 00:13:26.574
I remember there were times when we didn't have a lot, and my grandma would call—and she didn't know we didn't have food that night—and she'd say, "I have a pizza over here for you kids.

00:13:26.575 --> 00:13:33.669
I felt led to order you a pizza from Domino's."You would have thought we won the lottery.

00:13:33.670 --> 00:13:39.059
I'm telling you, I was so excited about that pizza. Ten dollars, man, but it was a lot.

00:13:39.060 --> 00:13:52.269
It got us through two days. We were so excited because we'd eat half of the pizza and have the other half later. It was a medium. Back then, oh man, that's a huge deal.

00:13:52.270 --> 00:14:26.729
