00:15:59.279 --> 00:16:15.411
My word stands alone. It's a pillar. Be obedient to what I've asked you to do."That was like swallowing sandburs.

00:16:15.412 --> 00:16:26.567
I didn't want to do it. But I could see as I was in obedience, things started to fall...

00:16:26.568 --> 00:16:34.398
but in disobedience, things started to fall apart. It opened doors and you could start seeing the cankerworm coming in.

00:16:34.399 --> 00:16:44.159
When the cankerworm comes in, you're going, "Why are things getting eaten?"Because the Bible says those that are willing and obedient will eat the good of the land.

00:16:44.160 --> 00:16:53.099
When you're willing and obedient, you'll eat the good of the land.

00:16:53.100 --> 00:16:57.439
But when you're not willing and you're not obedient to what He's asked you to do, you won't eat the good of the land.

00:16:57.440 --> 00:17:07.327
