00:17:07.328 --> 00:17:16.479
Where I'm going is that I see a wave of the glory on people, but God wants you just to say, "Yes, follow the voice of God.

00:17:16.480 --> 00:17:21.749
Be led by His Spirit in these last days,"and say, "Yes, here am I, Lord.

00:17:21.750 --> 00:17:38.079
